      <t>   This document defines a new ORF-type, called the "Covering Prefixes
   ORF (CP-ORF)".  CP-ORF is applicable in Virtual Hub-and-Spoke VPNs.
   It also is applicable in BGP/MPLS Ethernet VPN (EVPN) Networks.


